  "verification_notes": "Buzz Williams completed his first season (2025-26) as head coach after being hired April 1, 2025 from Texas A&M to replace Kevin Willard (who left for Villanova). Maryland finished 12-21 (4-16 Big Ten), eliminated in Big Ten Tournament Second Round vs Iowa; did NOT make NCAA Tournament. Roster shown is the 2025-26 season-end roster. Significant offseason turnover: notable departures via transfer portal include Darius Adams; reported incoming 2026-27 transfers include DJ Wagner (Arkansas), Tomislav Buljan (New Mexico), Robert Jennings (Oklahoma State), Bishop Boswell (Tennessee), plus freshman Baba Oladotun. Career head coaching record for Buzz Williams not verified — left null. Xfinity Center opened in 2002 (originally Comcast Center, renamed 2014). 2026-27 schedule TBD; Maryland confirmed return to Players Era Festival.",
